/* Use this format for the entry headers:
   YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM UTC[-|+]hhmm Your Full Name <your_email@address>
   For example:
   2002-12-01 16:55 UTC+0100 Foo Bar <foo.bar@foobar.org>
*/

/*
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 Old changelogs are archived in directory
 "oldlogs".
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
*/

